-- Qatar Awards Mitsubishi $260 Million Water Plant Contract
-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 2013-01-08T10:05:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-07/qatar-awards-mitsubishi-260-million-water-plant-contract.html
(Corrects story first published
yesterday to say project value is $500 million)
Qatar Electricity and Water Co agrees with govt utility Qatar
General Electricity and Water Corp., or Kahramaa, to build $500m
water desalination plant.
* Mitsubishi Corp. wins contract to build plant
* Qatar National Bank to finance 50%  of project
* Qatar Islamic, Barwa Bank, Al Rayan to finance remainder
* 36m gal/day plant to be finished by June 2015.
* QEWC GM Fahad al Mohannadi speaks in interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
